man I hate seeing ads after I've already bought
I hate seeing stuff I want on sale when I'm broke!

Oh, the prices on many looked pretty good but if you have better deals, PLEASE share with our fishing friends. We all need to save a buck these days. And with Christmas coming I thought this might be helpful.
Thanks Bobby Good to see you are still out there being our finacial watchdog The way i look at it is, a buck left in my pocket, is better than in theirs.

Just saying - those are not rock bottom yet - wait until Jan/Feb and Cabelas usually has crazy deals on electronics and map chips. I can see you are trying to help - I didn't mean to offend you. Sorry. Landry
No offense was taken.......just saying to post deals if you have some, especially before Christmas.....
